Please do these a few days before the course starts. Write to us in case of any questions. 
- Bring a laptop
- Download and install Anaconda. Follow the instructions below for that:
	1. Install Anaconda to your laptop here: https://www.anaconda.com/products/distribution and run it by double clicking
	2. Open the terminal to make sure you’re ready
		a) For mac: type terminal in your search and click on it. Next step will take a while: In terminal, type xcode-select --install 
		b) For windows: open a terminal in Anaconda prompt. If it opens, you’re all set.
